# .env.example
# Jones Barber Shop — environment variable reference
#
# This site is currently fully static with no backend.
# No environment variables are required to run the site locally.
#
# If a booking backend or contact form API is added in the future,
# add variables here as placeholders (never real values).
#
# Example (do not use real values):
# BOOKING_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
# CONTACT_FORM_ENDPOINT=https://your-form-handler.example.com
